article_title: Fire Rescue Units Repond To Car vs. Motorcycle Incident On Clearlake Road
article_text:
PHOTOS: Fire Rescue Units Repond To Car vs. Motorcycle Incident On Clearlake Road

By Space Coast Daily // August 22, 2015

ONE TRAUMA ALERT, ONE MINOR INJURY

Car vs. motorcycle Lake and Clearlake Rd. Trauma Alert. W.Cocoa. BCFR 44 units, Cocoa, D45 responded. pic.twitter.com/dX9MbaNL36 — BCFRpio (@BCFRpio) August 22, 2015

Fire Rescue Units reponded to a car vs. motorcycle incident at Lake and Clearlake Road today at about 4:30 p.m. Brevard County Fire Rescue West Cocoa units, Cocoa Fire, First Flight and District 45 responded to one trauma alert and one minor injury.
